Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you at least have worn your blazer to the opening ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, you're his older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be the one telling him this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossoms are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are. They're in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, you've got a petal on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, you've got a petal on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to get it for you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I wanted you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who our teacher will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's Taiazuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We met that spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We spent many seasons together after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's another beautiful spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We entered our second year at Homare High School this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I spy someone spending a hundred yen just for some oolong tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got plenty of barley tea in my fridge at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna buy oolong tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you might as well get milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You've gotta get your calcium intake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're always pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, I'm sure you'll end up buying love with money, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't get how you guys ended up there just from buying one oolong tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go up to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This whirlwind of sakura petals,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or rather, this spring clouded by dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}can't begin to satiate the hunger of us growing boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who suggested we eat lunch on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But the weather's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste to eat in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bigger waste if my food gets covered in sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take one of my sandwiches if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to give Kaname anything, Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just eat them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, why are you making such a fuss over a couple of pieces of food?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just buying some \Noolong tea like some rich kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off my back,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you two twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of getting mixed up in your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it's covered in sand, \Nit'll all be the same in my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when we invited you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you should have refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kaname-kun, Yuuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time you've \Nbeen in the same class, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this guy ignores anyone who tries to talk to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intentionally ignore anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Their words simply don't resonate with me.{I just don't hear them.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You just aren't listening to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it isn't hurting anyone, who cares if he's a lone wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Being ignored is plenty hurtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki's not nearly accommodating enough nor considerate enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotta be more... you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, you're such an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be so much cuter.{split this}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you calling cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, back when Kaname had feelings for Kaori-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that was pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling in love with your preschool \Nteacher is a little precocious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your innocent little eyes sparkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The reflective lenses of his glasses sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are ones to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys used to be cute little brats,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,getting all excited over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the person in the middle loses years off their lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta-kun's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta won't die as long as we don't forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my lifespan really decrease that quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this my last night on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I'll sleep in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking on someone else's life is a heavy burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All my courage has...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought of a way we can all live...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...without anyone getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm already hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask Kaname-kun to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping in the middle shortens your lifespan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you invited me over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's an even number of us, there technically isn't a middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can sleep in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this mean both of us are in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If identical twins lie side-by-side,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,then we only really count as one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep when I'm not next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Being twins is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For us, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that might've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get any sleep with you two around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun, you can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaori-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I sing you a lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat me like a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You made Shun sleep in the middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,just so you could sleep next to Kaori-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The innocence in your eyes \Nbegan to cloud over that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki, go join a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the fastest way for you \Nto get what you're missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You here to watch? No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to play a game with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A club's not something you force yourself into.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't force you to join, you never will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I already participate in club activities daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Going Home Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,YuUki-kun, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get the sweat, passion, and teamwork...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's missing from your high school experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what to do when \Nyou have the ball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurl it as hard as I can at you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You pass it to your teammates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki-kun obviously doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Asaba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you supposed to play on a team like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You never tried very hard in PE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just not really athletic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you seriously give basketball a go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I would, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really do suck that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you should join the Basketball Club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We play a lot of basketball in PE, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start the second half!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki's extremely athletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's even more amazing when he actually tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's even better than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole basketball club can't even keep up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki-kun's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so great about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No girl could keep her mouth \Nshut after seeing moves like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so cool about being a ball hog?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid suddenly grabbed my collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he wanted something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He was doing what you'd call "judo."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimming, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it keeps your shoulders from getting stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should think about my future health.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you unable to live in the present?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That would end in total rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who am I supposed to shoot at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The target!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Why can't you make up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to see more of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like my eyes are being forced open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuma-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A club for Yuuki-kun to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't make up his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already checked out \Nmost of the athletics clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Athletics clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really athletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Yuuta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think he should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki should decide for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should check out the other clubs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't always want \Nto do what they're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuma-sensei is really adult-like.{mature}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he is an adult, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Cooking Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Should we—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? Yuuta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the Cooking Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But Azuma-sensei said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In a middle school cooking class, Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuuki-kun, could you help us peel potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You start by holding the knife like this, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your knife back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki-kun, do you want to \Ncheck out the Tea Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, you're almost perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki, you're up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki-kun, it's fine if you wanna take it easy today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't remember where Kaname put his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wiped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want my indirect kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted an indirect kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What a creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname's part of the—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't want to do it, then he'll never choose a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're in no position to be reading manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that I love manga and anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The tea cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, you're paying for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, you're his brother! You must've known!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You made us waste all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This club will suit you perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk all you want about manga and anime here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them to stamp your admission form and turn it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you mad at Kaname-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's forcing you to join a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been awfully hard on him today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun's just worried about you in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in the middle shortens your lifespan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to sleep next to your beloved Kaori-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure the moment, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about it and decide who'll be in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun, I didn't know you cared so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun showed me he cared a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was because Yuuta and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about it and decide who'll be in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun, I didn't know you cared so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanme-kun has always cared about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get that stamp and get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our 17th spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That spring, something unchanging and something that's begun to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...intertwined like fluttering cherry blossom petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like the Going Home Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really join that club?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks! This was all pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But look...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to achieve your goal of getting Yuuki-kun to join a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an 80% chance nothing will change, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure there'll be plenty of changes to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "The Day the Tulips Blossomed".
